## Quick Start

{{ install }}

Import the ROM, then play or evaluate the immutable checkpoint:

```bash
uv run rlab import-roms ~/roms --game {{ game }}
uv run rlab play {{ model_ref }}
uv run rlab eval run {{ model_ref }}
```

